Class SimpleRegionObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.SimpleRegionObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Coprocessor, RegionCoprocessor, RegionObserver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestCoprocessorHost.SimpleRegionObserverV2, TestIncrementTimeRange.MyObserver, TestNegativeMemStoreSizeWithSlowCoprocessor.FlushingRegionObserver, TestRegionServerCoprocessorExceptionWithAbort.BuggyRegionObserver, TestRegionServerCoprocessorExceptionWithRemove.BuggyRegionObserver

    public class SimpleRegionObserver
extends Object
implements RegionCoprocessor, RegionObserver
    A sample region observer that tests the RegionObserver interface. It works with TestRegionObserverInterface to provide the test case.
